	<div class="container">
		<h1 class="text-center mt-4 mb-5">How HairHubApp Works?</h1>
    <div class="container2" style= "background-color: #e3f2fd; padding: 20px; border:5px solid #ccc; border-radius: 8px;">
      <h2>For Individuals</h2><br>
      <ol>
        <li>Register an account: To use HairHubApp, you need to register and create an account. This will allow you to research agencies that match what you are looking for.</li>
        <li>Connect with agencies: Once you are logged in, you can connect with agencies around the world by searching on a map by location or by agency name.</li>
        <li>Reach out to agencies: When you find an offer that matches your requirements, you can reach out to the agency and they will respond whether they will accept or reject the offer.</li>
        <li>Private chat: A private chat will be available for you both to stay in contact.</li>
        <li>Payment: After agreement, Stripe API payment will be available to complete the transaction.</li>
      </ol>
      <br>
      <div style="display: flex; justify-content: flex-end;">
       <%= link_to "Sign Up Individual", new_user_registration_path, class:"btn btn-info" %>
      </div>
    </div><br>
    <div class="container2" style= "background-color: #e3f2fd; padding: 20px; border:5px solid #ccc; border-radius: 8px;">
      <h2 >For Hair Agencies</h2><br>
      <ol>
        <li>Register: If you are a hair agency, you will need to register as an Agency.</li>
        <li>Submit application: After registering, you can pay a subscription to register your agency with us. Mandatory private documentation must be provided.</li>
        <li>Map search: A map will be available to search for your agency manually and register it as your own business.</li>
        <li>Request verification: Once you find your agency, you can request to verify it as yours. Regulatory documentation must be provided for verification.</li>
      </ol>
      <br>
      <div style="display: flex; justify-content: flex-end;">
        <%= link_to "Sign Up  As Agency", new_owner_registration_path, class:"btn btn-info" %>
      </div>
    </div> <br>
	</div> <br> <br>

<div class="jumbotron jumbotron-fluid" style="background-image: url('<%= asset_path('backgroundform.png') %>'); background-color: #e3f2fd; padding: 20px; border:5px solid #ccc; border-radius: 8px;">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row align-items-center">
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <%= image_tag("Wehelp.png",style:"width: 22rem;", class:"rounded-circle") %>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-8">
        <div class="card rounded" style="background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h2 class="card-title mb-5">How Can We Help?</h2>
            <form>
              <div class="form-group rounded">
                <label for="name">Name:</label>
                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="name" placeholder="Enter your name">
              </div>
              <div class="form-group rounded">
                <label for="email">Email address:</label>
                <input type="email" class="form-control" id="email" placeholder="Enter your email">
              </div>
              <div class="form-group rounded">
                <label for="subject">Subject:</label>
                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="subject" placeholder="Enter subject">
              </div>
              <div class="form-group rounded">
                <label for="message">Message:</label>
                <textarea class="form-control" rows="5" id="message" placeholder="Enter your message"></textarea>
              </div>
              <div style="display: flex; justify-content: center;">
               <button type="submit" class="btn btn-outline-info my-6 my-sm-0">Submit</button>
              </div>
            </form>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
